docs {
  # Undo Enable Next Week (Button 3 — undo)

  Restores the year suspension back to next Monday (reverses Enable Next Week Only).
  Sets suspendedFrom = next Monday and removes any next-week cancellation.
  Available before Sunday 10:30 AM IST.
}
